d":77811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"係唔收冇生產力嘅難民喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放香港人嚟做野，當地人就拎褔利"},{"pid":"8ad17991eab6786a68bbab378e4ff22b9a1665f4","tid":2095283,"uid":287211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:37:27.000Z","msg":"酸到呢！ ph值都驗唔到"},{"pid":"ac410d3268efd423da45ec97ba9163cbd6d38b9c","tid":2095283,"uid":3967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"乜嘢都係小人之心, 正宗小農DNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}